name: The Mind Meetup
description:
okay Alixos, so what's the point with all this mind thing?

It all started with a drawing, there's the main character with the green hair. And there's the other character with the pink hair, you can say its "the-other-self". The one that whispers thoughts. Sometimes its a darker thoughts.

The Main Character are affected by what The Other Character said, that she focused more on her mind and finally be able to properly communicat  with The Other Character.

The Other Character is not a villain. You can say its like that Inner Child we all have. It needs to be nurtured.

So that's the story of all this Mind Things. Let's nurture our own inner child, shall we?

Love,
Alixos
